summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 9, 10, 11 and 12, Block 22, Graff's Salmon Bay Addition; Also, Lots 14 and 15, Block 1, Herbert S. Upper's 1st Replat of Lincoln Beach Addition; Also, all of Block 11, Hill Tract Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections, numbered 2-26 and 17-21.
